	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vehementer doluit, frater in domino venerande, quod non licuit maiori vos prosequi benevolentia et humanitate<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Zum Besuch von <persName ref="154">Myconius</persName> und <persName ref="81">Grynäus</persName> in Zürich s. oben <ref target="file#10918">Nr. 877</ref>, 5-30.</note>; certe voluntas non defuit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc, quid <placeName ref="121">Bernae</placeName> impetraveritis<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Vgl. den Bericht der <placeName ref="121">Berner</placeName> Pfarrer über die Verhandlungen vom 17. August, oben <ref target="file#10919">Nr. 878</ref>.</note>, scire cupimus.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid doctor bannes <persName ref="263">Zviccius</persName> a <placeName ref="565">Constantia</placeName> scripserit<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Oben <ref target="file#10920">Nr. 879</ref>.</note> hic habetis., Quodsi vestrates conventum cogere volunt generalem, consultissimum tum propter causam tum propter nos videtur, si post nundinas hoc agant Francfordianas<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Die <placeName ref="361">Frankfurter</placeName> Herbstmesse fand in der Regel zwischen Mariä Himmelfahrt (15. August) und Mariä Geburt (8. September) statt; s. Alexander <hi>Dietz,</hi> <placeName ref="361">Frankfurter</placeName> Handelsgeschichte, Bd. I, <placeName ref="361">Frankfurt</placeName> a. M. 1910, S. 37-40.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim enim <persName ref="226">Vadiani</persName> libros recipiet <persName ref="138">Lutherus</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. oben <ref target="file#10922">Nr. 881</ref>, 6f.</note> palamque, quid animo volvat, exponet.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certe - ut libere, quod sentio, dicam - videtur unus <persName ref="263">Zviccius</persName> planius negotium hoc exposuisse quam <placeName ref="1049">Argentoratenses</placeName>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectamus a vobis responsionem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="81">Grynaeum</persName>, ecclesiarum decus, ex me salutabis diligentissime.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Huic communicabis perpetuo, quae scribo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valebitis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">24. Augusti 1536.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus per omnia</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">H. Bullingerus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
